snippet.title: Coreborn - Full Release Trailer
snippet.description:
🎮 GET IT NOW on Steam: https://bit.ly/WishlistCoreborn

💬 Join Coreborn Discord for updates and playtests: https://discord.gg/blankhans

Coreborn is a multiplayer survival game set in the open world of Ultracore. Build, grow, and defend your town. Survive the elements and Sorgoth’s onslaught. Cooperate as you go on adventures.

Follow Coreborn
Twitter | Instagram | TikTok: @Blankhans
